  diff for objects
- `FactLockModal.jsx` — create lock (permission-gated)
- `ConflictResolveModal.jsx` — three-button resolution UI

Diff viewer uses `diff` library (already in package.json for docs tab;
if not, add to package.json). For JSON values, use a recursive tree
diff showing added/removed/modified keys in crimson/cyan/amber.

Conflict rows render with a red left border + "PENDING REVIEW" badge.
Click opens `ConflictResolveModal` with three buttons (keep_lock,
accept_collector, edit_lock). Non-admin users see read-only modal.

