## Change 5 — Diff viewer

`gui/src/components/FactDiffViewer.jsx`:

- Props: `{priorValue, newValue, priorTimestamp, newTimestamp, source, actor}`
- Header: "Changed at <newTimestamp> by <source>"
- Body:
  - If both values are strings → character-level diff with added/removed
    highlighted
  - If both are numbers → "23 → 42" with delta
  - If both are arrays → show removed items in crimson, added items in
    cyan, unchanged in muted text
  - If both are objects → recursive tree diff, modified leaves highlighted

Extensible: the diff renderer accepts a `valueType` prop so future
config-file diffs (switch config, firewall rules) can plug in with a
custom renderer. Note this in the component docstring.

